{"tid":1094852,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！下一作《刺客信條》有機會是維京主題，代號“Kingdom”","createTime":"2019-04-06T15:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T08:28:48.000Z","uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6837abc1d2f350314338fa0560a89eafb537d167","tid":1094852,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kotaku.com/odd-tease-in-the-division-2-spills-the-beans-on-the-nex-1833838193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkotaku.com%2Fodd-tease-in-the-division-2-spills-the-beans-on-the-nex-1833838193&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=951705c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://kotaku.com/odd-tease-in-the-division-2-spills-the-beans-on-the-nex-1833838193</a><br />\n在[育碧宣布2019年不會推出《刺客信條》新作]後，關於系列下一作將以哪段歷史為背景的討論就不曾停止過，比如此前就有爆料稱[羅馬將會是新《刺客信條》的主舞台]<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--PjFm9H6N--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/ushcw1six7c1vohyfrnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--PjFm9H6N--%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Fushcw1six7c1vohyfrnf.jpg&h=e71de01d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而在近日，一張《全境封鎖2》中的海報又給這個問題帶來了新的可能：維京將成為系列新作的主題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--yN3BzUYH--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/muqdqcn21mi9qstymfua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--yN3BzUYH--%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Fmuqdqcn21mi9qstymfua.jpg&h=4a2f5532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這張海報出現在《全境封鎖2》內波托馬克活動中心，最吸引人注意的是，圖中人物所手持的伊甸蘋果。考慮到育碧一直有在遊戲裡放未來新作彩蛋的傳統，這一《刺客信條》系列關鍵科技的出現自然讓人浮想聯翩，而正上方的'Valhalla'(瓦爾哈拉)則暗示了新作為維京主題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/s--g4EjaNuV--/c_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,q_80,w_800/czrho7rol2ltqus9pthu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kinja-img.com%2Fgawker-media%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fs--g4EjaNuV--%2Fc_scale%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_800%2Fczrho7rol2ltqus9pthu.jpg&h=f33e5188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，外媒Kotaku編輯Jason Schreier也證實了這一傳言的可信度，他在幾個月前通過兩個熟悉該遊戲的獨立信息渠道獲悉，《刺客信條》新作代號為&ldquo;Kingdom&rdquo;，主題正是&ldquo;維京&rdquo;。並且他再次確認《看門狗3》的故事將發生在倫敦，這也和[《看門狗2》更新補丁所暗示的內容相符合]。<br />\n<br />\n目前，育碧拒絕對此事發表評論。各位怎麼看待《刺客信條》的故事發生在維京時代呢？"},{"pid":"71f932915761d0998ee5d9af0e79816971d85689","tid":1094852,"uid":195438,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"好憎刺客嘅一樣嘢，Open過頭，成日玩玩下已經唔清楚個主線UP緊乜"},{"pid":"7cd33453a598f6ff5bd80271cfc8cbd6eb591006","tid":1094852,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:23:50.000Z","msg":"看門狗3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8433d16c472cf67657a65402085cbd9a16c732","tid":1094852,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:25:23.000Z","msg":"悶"},{"pid":"4995568f283d224bc4e91d132eafefba9e3333ea","tid":1094852,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"建議整香港 🇭🇰"},{"pid":"1279de1c3bf9746bf86c254b7a83f534138a3575","tid":1094852,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"建議整太空"},{"pid":"edea8fc1ca8cf9caf4194248ac209c928ed36327","tid":1094852,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":24,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">是</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkViFMC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkViFMC.png&h=fe1bce54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1aae16f6fa8658526537b3ce49e3a466a7064681","tid":10948